---
description: Block schema, migration, deploy, and production automation in Sophex setup
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

No Prisma migrate, db push, migrate resolve, destructive DDL, schema creation, generated-client edits, or production database commands are allowed in this setup lane.

No deploy commands, production services, provider sends, queue launches, R2/Docling runtime, MotherDuck/vector runtime, CRE production lane, or Fabricator runtime work is allowed.

If a request needs any of the above, stop and ask for explicit operator approval in the correct lane.
